Feature: Register an employee
Description: Admin registers an
employee
Actor: Admin
# Main scenario
Scenario: Register a new employee
Given that the admin is logged in
And there is no employee with ID "mkr"
When register an employee with
Name "Malthe K. Reuber", e-mail
"s203869@student.dtu.dk" and employee
ID "mkr"
Then the person is an registered
employee of the system with ID "mkr"
# Alternative scenario
Scenario: Register an employee with an
already existing employee ID
Given that the admin is logged in
And there is an employee with ID "mkr"
When register an employee with
Name "Malthe K. Reuber", e-mail
"s203869@student.dtu.dk" and employee
ID "mkr"
Then the error message "Employee ID
already taken" is given